{"title":"MIPS Integra teases more integrated helmet protection, renames Air, Evolve & Essential","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/02/mips-integra-teases-more-integrated-helmet-protection-renames-air-evolve-essential/","date":1612283620000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-3\"></span>MIPS has given their anti-rotation, friction-layer helmet safety systems a naming overhaul to make it easier to differentiate levels of protection &amp; performance, and at the same time unveiled a new Integra system to be built seamlessly into new helmets.&nbsp;MIPS Air, Evolve &amp; Essential are simply new names to better highlight the current MIPS systems, but Integra is an all-new in-mold solution, plus a new Elevate system we won’t see in bike helmets.</p><h2>MIPS Integra, an extra level of integrated helmet protection</h2><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_impact-testing.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_impact-testing.jpg\" alt=\"MIPS Integra new integrated helmet protection, rotation-reduction, yellow low-friction liner, crash test\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_impact-testing.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protectio