mets_impact-testing-747x420.jpg 747w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_impact-testing.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_impact-testing-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_impact-testing-800x450.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_impact-testing-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_impact-testing-768x432.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_impact-testing-1536x864.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_impact-testing-696x392.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_impact-testing-1068x601.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_impact-testing-747x420.jpg 747w\"></a></p><p>The new MIPS&nbsp;Integra solution claims to be the brand’s “most integrated” MIPS helmet protection system yet. The new idea here is to actually co-mold their signature yellow low-friction layer directly into the helmet’s EPS foam structure – much like a polycarbonate shell is molded from the outside.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail.jpg\" alt=\"MIPS Integra new integrated helmet protection, rotation-reduction, yellow low-friction liner, new safer cycling helmets, inmold MIPS detail\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail-1536x1152.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail-1068x801.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail-265x198.jpg 265w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail-1536x1152.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail-1068x801.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Integra-new-integrated-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_new-safer-cycling-helmets_cutaway-detail-265x198.jpg 265w\"></a></p><p>That is said to allow the helmet’s padding to slide against the low-friction layer for a lower-profile solution, without interfering at all with a helmet’s ventilation channels. It does however seem to only be able to reduce rotational forces in certain impact angles.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-3\"></span></p><p>So far, MIPS hasn’t mentioned any helmet to feature the new Integra tech, or even show a real set of pads inside, so we’re unsure when to expect consumer availability. But MIPS is calling it one of their “lightest and slimmest systems”, said to have been co-developed with a favorite helmet brand.</p><p><iframe width=\"696\" height=\"392\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\" data-ezsrc=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/504922313\"></iframe></p><h3>MIPS helmet system reclassification: Essential, Evolve, Air, Integra &amp; Elevate</h3><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Limar-Air-Pro-MIPS-Ai-road-helmet_next-gen-MIPS-impact-protection-in-fully-vented-aero-road-bike-helmet_inside.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1100\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Limar-Air-Pro-MIPS-Ai-road-helmet_next-gen-MIPS-impact-protection-in-fully-vented-aero-road-bike-helmet_inside.jpg\"><figcaption>c. Limar</figcaption></figure><p>The rationale behind renaming each MIPS iteration essentially comes down to making it easier for consumers to understand, especially as lower-cost &amp; higher-performance systems have been introduced. We saw the issue come to a head last fall when Limar referred to the lightweight protection in their Air Pro as <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/10/29/limar-air-pro-road-helmet-adds-extra-protection-with-all-new-mips-ai-tech-inside/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">MIPS Ai</a>, which was effectively the same system Specialized had called <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2018/11/28/specialized-helmets-get-safer-with-angi-smart-sensor-mips-proprietary-mips-sl/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">MIPS SL</a>. That system now has an official name: MIPS Air.</p><figure id=\"attachment_250868\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-250868\"><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Essential-Evolve-Air-Integra-Elevate-helmet-protection-renaming_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_small-examples.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Essential-Evolve-Air-Integra-Elevate-helmet-protection-renaming_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_small-examples.jpg\" alt=\"MIPS Essential Evolve Air Integra helmet protection renaming, rotation-reduction, safer helmets\" width=\"1000\" height=\"350\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Essential-Evolve-Air-Integra-Elevate-helmet-protection-renaming_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_small-examples.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Essential-Evolve-Air-Integra-Elevate-helmet-protection-renaming_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_small-examples.jpg 1000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Essential-Evolve-Air-Integra-Elevate-helmet-protection-renaming_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_small-examples-297x104.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Essential-Evolve-Air-Integra-Elevate-helmet-protection-renaming_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_small-examples-800x280.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Essential-Evolve-Air-Integra-Elevate-helmet-protection-renaming_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_small-examples-120x42.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Essential-Evolve-Air-Integra-Elevate-helmet-protection-renaming_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_small-examples-768x269.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Essential-Evolve-Air-Integra-Elevate-helmet-protection-renaming_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_small-examples-696x244.jpg 696w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Essential-Evolve-Air-Integra-Elevate-helmet-protection-renaming_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_small-examples.jpg 1000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Essential-Evolve-Air-Integra-Elevate-helmet-protection-renaming_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_small-examples-297x104.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Essential-Evolve-Air-Integra-Elevate-helmet-protection-renaming_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_small-examples-800x280.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Essential-Evolve-Air-Integra-Elevate-helmet-protection-renaming_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_small-examples-120x42.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Essential-Evolve-Air-Integra-Elevate-helmet-protection-renaming_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_small-examples-768x269.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Essential-Evolve-Air-Integra-Elevate-helmet-protection-renaming_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_small-examples-696x244.jpg 696w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-250868\">MIPS Essential, Evolve, Air &amp; Integra (l-r)</figcaption></figure><p>Of the five renamed levels of MIPS protection, four will be found in cycling helmets. Essential delivers the most low-cost solution – all of the protection but sacrificing weight &amp; ventilation. Evolve is the bread &amp; butter of what we see as MIPS in bike helmets – improved fit, lighter weight, better ventilation &amp; integration with dial retention setups. Air is that newer, lighter system above – replying on slip-layer pads attached to the helmet with stretchy rubber anchors to get unrestricted ventilation. And then, Integra promises the most seamless fit &amp; performance.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Essential-Evolve-Air-Integra-Elevate-helmet-protection-renaming_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_safer-helmets.jpg\"><img load