h system Elevate is actually quite interesting, even though it is limited to worker safety hardhats. MIPS simply developed a rotation-reducing insert that fits the standard hard hat helmet harness setup, adding a further layer of protection in hazardous industrial workplaces.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Evolve-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_safer-helmets-testing.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Evolve-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_safer-helmets-testing.jpg\" alt=\"MIPS Essential Evolve Air Integra Elevate helmet protection renaming, rotation-reduction, safer helmets\" width=\"1200\" height=\"720\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Evolve-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_safer-helmets-testing.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Evolve-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_safer-helmets-testing.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Evolve-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_safer-helmets-testing-297x178.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Evolve-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_safer-helmets-testing-800x480.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Evolve-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_safer-helmets-testing-120x72.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Evolve-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_safer-helmets-testing-768x461.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Evolve-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_safer-helmets-testing-696x418.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Evolve-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_safer-helmets-testing-1068x641.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Evolve-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_safer-helmets-testing-700x420.jpg 700w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Evolve-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_safer-helmets-testing.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Evolve-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_safer-helmets-testing-297x178.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Evolve-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_safer-helmets-testing-800x480.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Evolve-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_safer-helmets-testing-120x72.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Evolve-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_safer-helmets-testing-768x461.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Evolve-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_safer-helmets-testing-696x418.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Evolve-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_safer-helmets-testing-1068x641.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MIPS-Evolve-helmet-protection_rotation-reduction_yellow-low-friction-liner_safer-helmets-testing-700x420.jpg 700w\"></a></p><p>While MIPS’ business model revolves around selling to helmet makers, not end-users, this renaming is an attempt by the Swedish safety company to offer a “more consumer-centric brand identity.”</p><h3>Other MIPS tech?</h3><p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Giro-Aether-MIPS-Spherical-road-helmet-cycling-review-actual-weight-10.jpg\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Giro-Aether-MIPS-Spherical-road-helmet-cycling-review-actual-weight-10.jpg\"></p><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-4\"></span>Interestingly, with four new names for MIPS protection tech for cycling (plus Elevate for hardhats), <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=mips+spherical\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">MIPS Spherical</a> doesn’t really fit in anywhere here. MIPS Spherical is maybe an even more integrated system than Integra. Already available now in the Giro <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2018/07/02/hands-on-impressive-giro-aether-cycling-helmet-brings-mips-spherical-to-the-road/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Aether</a>, <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2019/08/05/giro-tyrant-rules-the-roost-with-full-cut-mtb-style-mips-spherical-protection/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Tyrant</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/11/17/all-new-giro-helios-adds-another-spherical-helmet-option-for-road-or-gravel/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Helios</a> helmets, it uses a helmet-in-helmet construction rather than the yellow low-friction layer like in the other helmets above to deliver similar rotational impact protection in a crash.</p><p><a href=\"http://mipsprotection.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>MIPSprotection.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"45d9e282fee406cfd669b71429449b9c84bacb974f8c258dbe010927a4c73c84","category":"Cycling"}